class_description:
UnsupportedTemporalTypeException indicates that a ChronoField or ChronoUnit is
 not supported for a Temporal class.

params.param_description: the message to use for this exception, may be null

Methods.method_description: Constructs a new UnsupportedTemporalTypeException with the specified message.

params.param_description: the message to use for this exception, may be null
the cause of the exception, may be null

Methods.method_description: Constructs a new UnsupportedTemporalTypeException with the specified message and cause.
